cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for automatically searching over multi-task architectures while taking resource constraints into consideration. This involves optimizing for efficient multi-task models, which is a common theme in machine learning and artificial intelligence research (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The proposed method is benchmarked on Visual Decathlon, which is a computer vision dataset (cs.CV, cs.CL).
